<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٧٨١ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3960">‌عَبْدُ اللهِ بْنُ هَاشِمٍ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> ثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6931">‌يَحْيَى - يَعْنِي ابْنَ سَعِيدٍ </a>-<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٦٧⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6690">‌هِشَامٍ - يَعْنِي ابْنَ حَسَّانَ </a>-<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> ثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2789">‌شُعَيْبُ بْنُ الْحَبْحَابِ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">‌أَنَسٍ </a>رَضِيَ اللهُ عَنْهُ قَالَ: <span class="c2">«أَعْتَقَ رَسُولُ اللهِ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ صَفِيَّةَ وَأَصْدَقَهَا عِتْقَهَا»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>